Description: # pymontecarlo
        A small Python library for creating simple Monte Carlo simulations.
        
        ## Installation
        ```bash
        pip install montecarlo
        ```
        
        ## Usage
        (Under construction)
        ```python
        from montecarlo import montecarlo
        
        def setup():
            ...
        
        def test():
            if (...):
                return True
            return False
        
        mc = montecarlo(test, setup=setup)
        mc.run(iterations=100000)
        ```
        
